text: Louise Fribo is a singer from Denmark who also recorded the Danish language versions of the movies Mary Poppins (movie), The Little Mermaid II: Return to the Sea, Beauty and the Beast (1991 movie), and The Little Mermaid: Ariel’s beginning.
